      <description>&lt;DIV&gt;Since the conversation has been predominantly about server mergers lately, I wanted to take the time to start a thread on other issues that you consider important on the Zek servers.&amp;nbsp; For the most part, we're just going round and round on the server merging threads and until we are provided with more details, such as a date for a merger or other details ironed out, it will be difficult to make much headway.&amp;nbsp; &lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;What other issues are each of you encountering that may need addressed? The main other items that I have seen discussed are :&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;-hacking problems needing to be dealt with&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;-pvp spell resists needing to be implemented for spells over level 65&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;Another &amp;nbsp;issue mentioned by members of a couple servers were :&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;-the sk spell dread gaze (ae terror spell) aggroing pets of the members of your raids.&amp;nbsp; The most suggested solution to this was to make the spell similar to wizard ae spells so that if you're in the raid, it doesn't affect pets of members of the raid.&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;Any other pressing issues besides the main items on the Issues list that feel need to be addressed currently? &lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
